Company Overview of ViaHero, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
ViaHero, LLC operates an online open marketplace that connects travelers with local planning experts for their trips. Its platform enables users to tell about their travel preferences; browse and pick the local trip planners based on their profiles and daily rates; receive a personalized trip guide; and get recommendations about food, drinks, sights, events, activities, and more, as well as logistics and booking info from trip planners. The company was founded in 2015 and is based in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania.


