ViaHero | Become a Hero
















































How it Works







Become a Hero
Interested in becoming a Hero? Now accepting applications to become a Hero in Cuba, Iceland and Japan!

Hero Application

What will I be doing?
Customers will request your trip planning services and you’ll work with them to build a personalized Trip Plan. This includes recommendations for places to eat, activities, booking and transportation information, and info about the destination(s). You'll use our Trip Plan app to create amazing trips!
What's the process?

ViaHero will review your completed application to vet your knowledge of the area. We accept <5% of applications.
You'll create a sample trip plan for each country you intend to focus on.
If accepted, we’ll get you set up on our platform and start the ViaHero training process.

What are you waiting for?







































