How to fly to Cuba. The latest updates on everything you need to know about flights to Cuba, including flying from the US to Cuba.







Lodging
Where to stay in Cuba. Information about the range of lodging options, plus how to book lodging in Cuba.







Everything About Transportation In Cuba
How to get around in Cuba. Everything to know about transportation in Cuba including public transport, taxis, buses, trains, and car rentals in Cuba.







Cuban Tourist Cards & Visas
Information on how to get a Cuban tourist card and visa in Cuba and what the difference is between the two. How to get a tourist card from the US.







The Definitive Guide to Cuba's Two Currencies
Learn everything about Money in Cuba for travelers.  How to exchange CUC and CUP, including with US Dollars.







Food in Cuba: The Best Things to Eat and Where to Eat Them
Information on the different types of food in Cuba and types of restaurant options. Covering the entire budget spectrum from street food to fine dining.







Phone & Internet in Cuba
How to use the internet in Cuba. Everything you need to know about getting access to the internet or phone calls in Cuba.







Cuba FAQs
Other commonly asked questions about Cuba. When to go to Cuba, what to bring to Cuba, the latest on Zika in Cuba, power outlets in Cuba and more.







