How it Works










 How It Works 



1
Match with a local(we call them Heroes!)

Share your travel preferences and we’ll suggest your best match. Then choose a Hero to plan your trip!











































2
Consult with your Hero


Work with your Hero via email. Once you agree on a basic itinerary, your Hero will begin building your Trip Plan in the Trip Plans app.

























3
Travel confidently


Travel independently with access to your personalized guidebook and custom map on mobile - no wifi or data necessary.







